":"ggHo-yWyVXU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/498276477_10162421500895090_2144661147588048849_n.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7uT70rLT8_text","label":"gg7uT70rLT8_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">The Perfect Gift for My Husband</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpcGRoEQhT_text","label":"ggpcGRoEQhT_text","default":"<p>The shirt came out way better than I expected. I ordered it with pictures of our two dogs for my husband and he literally just stood there smiling when he opened it. The colors were bright, the dogs looked so clear, and the whole thing felt really personal. He wore it the same night to dinner and everyone kept asking where I got it from. The only thing I would say is it took a little longer than I thought to arrive, but honestly it was worth the wait.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguY7QvohhM_text","label":"gguY7QvohhM_text","default":"<p>ron d.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2EiQA_kVZ_childItem_0","label":"gg2EiQA_kVZ_childItem_0","default":"<p>verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKp4y8aDpK_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggKp4y8aDpK_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_12_25_25.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbNlt912uz_text","label":"ggbNlt912uz_text","default":"My Dad Showed Everyone"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaIIux6kpV_text","label":"ggaIIux6kpV_text","default":"<p>I got this for my dad for Father’s Day and he absolutely loved it. He doesn’t usually get emotional over gifts but when he saw our old dog on the shirt he got quiet for a second and said “this is actually really cool.” That alone made it worth it. Thank you Hapyco.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghbdWf1S0I_text","label":"gghbdWf1S0I_text","default":"<p>Tommy G.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXodWLXYj9_childItem_0","label":"ggXodWLXYj9_childItem_0","default":"<p>verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvOiRjsRSc_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggvOiRjsRSc_srcS