ggiUNvvbYkT_childItem_0","label":"ggiUNvvbYkT_childItem_0","default":"<p>verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaplnOalc2_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaplnOalc2_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/ChatGPT_Image_24_juin_2026_13_00_52.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj55v5oBWj_text","label":"ggj55v5oBWj_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#000000;\">So Cute and Bright</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWpEm7o-W0_text","label":"ggWpEm7o-W0_text","default":"<p>Honestly I wasn’t sure how the photo would look on a Hawaiian shirt, but it came out so cute. The colors are bright, the fabric is light, and my dog’s face is everywhere in the funniest way. My husband has already worn it twice.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSo3tb0KO9_text","label":"ggSo3tb0KO9_text","default":"<p>John M.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqtOcmPD1Q_childItem_0","label":"ggqtOcmPD1Q_childItem_0","default":"<p>verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1AzXVMlQj_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg1AzXVMlQj_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/492009406_9305474039562079_4153155144964008448_n.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtb5aRMmlI_text","label":"ggtb5aRMmlI_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Strangers Kept Complimenting Him</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcmHQakp1d_text","label":"ggcmHQakp1d_text","default":"<p>Bought this for my fiancé and he loved it. We went out for drinks and strangers kept complimenting the shirt. He was proud telling everyone it was our dog on it. Such a cool idea and really good quality.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBEBA7Z0To_text","label":"ggBEBA7Z0To_text","default":"<p>Walt f.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSRlEt7zg6_childItem_0","label":"ggSRlEt7zg6_childItem_0","default":"<p>verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTzJSpgZ7w_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggTzJSpgZ7w_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/8d6d03bc-bbac-4820-9